cff-version: 1.2.0
message: "If you use Limboo in your work, please cite it using these metadata."
title: "Limboo"
abstract: >-
  Limboo is a local-first desktop application that acts as the operating system for
  AI software development. It provides the environment around a connected coding
  agent: workspaces, sessions, file watching, repository indexing, git operations,
  terminal execution, memory, permissions, and context.
type: software
authors:
